These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta
City: boston, berlin
The people have 2 different jobs:  fisherman, mechanic
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: superhero, western
There are 2 different favourite colors: blue, coral
2 different pets are kept: frog, turtle
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, subway
1. the person drinking cola is on the far right##1
2. the mechanic is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
4. the owner of the frog is the person who likes coral##1
5. the person watching western movies is on the far left##1
6. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |
| Beverage      | fanta     | cola       |
| City         | boston   | berlin     |
| Job           | fisherman | mechanic   |
| Movie-Genre   | western   | superhero  |
| Color   | coral | blue |
| Pet           | frog      | turtle     |
| Transport     | subway    | airplane   |

